### Get all items
GET http://localhost:5208/items

### Get item by id
GET http://localhost:5208/items/1

### Post a new item
POST http://localhost:5208/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Table",
  "description": "Wooden table",
  "price": 10.0
}

### Update an item
PUT http://localhost:5208/items/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Table",
  "description": "Wooden table",
  "price": 15.0
}

### Delete an item
DELETE http://localhost:5208/items/1